content.description: Sit start on a decent crimp rail and make a big move to a small crimp/slot and make a tough toss to a sloping hold.  pull to the top on better holds to a mild top-out.  stay direct.
content.location: to the right of DJ's Crimps on the main face of DJ boulder

content.description: Sit start deep in the tunnel feature on the small boulder to the right of the main face of DJ bolder.  Start on side pulls and pull crazy hard moves on crimps out the tunnel and top-out on easy ground.
content.location: in a hidden tunnel on the bolder to the right of DJ boulder.

content.description: In the Locker.  Sit start on a good pocket under the small boulder and traverse right on sloping pressure move to good holds at the arete and top-out.
content.location: In the Locker.  bellow the DJ boulder.  on the small boulder to the south side of the Locker.

content.description: Sit start on good holds and climb the prow to the right on good crimps.  Hit the jug and top-out.
content.location: On the Ant Farm boulder.  Follow a trail through some bushes to the right of the boulder next to Main face of DJ boulder.

content.description: Start on DJ's Block and climb to about 7ft and traverse left along crimps across the face to a large hueco at the top of the boulder just right of the tree and top-out.
content.location: starting on the right side of the main face of DJ boulder

content.description: Sit start on good holds at the base of the right leaning seam.  Climb the seam up and right.  Make cruxy move on crimps in the middle and finish on better holds.
content.location: Right of tree at the base of right leaning seam.  on main face of DJ boulder.

content.description: Sit start on good blocky low holds.  Climb up using a some good pockets and edges.
Start matched on a good crimp on the right side on the main face.  make a big dyno out the bulge to a jug and top it out.
content.location: right side of main face of DJ boulder

content.description: Sit Start on two somewhat smoothed crimps and climb the face on crimps.
content.location: to the right on the main face of DJ boulder

content.description: Start on the low block pinch and climb on good edges over the bulge and slightly left to the top.
content.location: right side of main face of DJ boulder

content.description: Sit start on the low slopey shelf. Climb up and slightly right using the arete and a bad sloper.  Hit the crimp and climb up and right using the pocket/pinches.  Holds up and left of the arete are off.
content.location: On the felt side of the main face of the Davey Jones Locker (DJ) boulder.  Just left of the tree.

content.description: Sit start on DJ's Seam but go straight up to the hueco and top-out.
content.location: at the base of the right leaning seam on the main face of DJ boulder.

content.description: A nice main boulder with hidden boulders below and around it.  Morning sun makes the and ideal spot to warm-up on a cold day.
